### Create a new game
# @name createGame
POST http://localhost:3001/api/game/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "hostName": "Tester",
  "hostId": "tester-user-1",
  "initialPrompt": "A traveler enters a mysterious forest...",
  "turnDurationSeconds": 60,
  "maxTurns": 3,
  "maxPlayers": 3,
  "mode": "multi"
}

### Join an existing game (1)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/game/{{createGame.response.body.game.id}}/join
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerName": "Player2",
  "playerId": "player2-user-1"
}

### Join an existing game (2)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/game/{{createGame.response.body.game.id}}/join
Content-Type: application/json

